          "description": "BROKEN ARM PT\nMy wife broke her arm and is being treated by Doctor at HSS. Now doing PT at the main building on east 70th st, second floor.\nVery poor entrance as this is an old crowded building. After entering, go left to pass security. Then to the check-in desk. PT for arm injuries is on second floor. Small waiting room is usually crowded as not enough chairs for all the patients. PT lady is very professional and prompt.\nPYRAMID CAFE\nAfter you check in on ground floor, there is a nice little cafe counter on the right side. I got an Americano Coffee and it was made just right. Sign says it is Starbucks coffee.\nThey also have pastries and other things.  Very busy spot for the two workers.  Glad it is here.",
