        {
          "username": "Candice Sturtevant",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "106747754770065002637",
          "user_review_count": 12,
          "user_photo_count": 9,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWb24hIzf9krgMHyrjWbrEWMp0bVpOfoU_sGnWV7-f1xLzFpxoz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "I just had my right hip replacement done with Dr. Westrich and can't recommend him and the entire team at HSS enough!! Every single person was attentive, compassionate and thorough. All systems ran so smoothly and efficiently from beginning to end. And although my surgery was just yesterday, I can already tell that my outcome is going to be wonderful compared to a not great experience at another facility for my left side. Moving forward I will not go anywhere else for my orthopedic needs! Thank you all so very much!",
