          "description": "I had my TKR(Total Knee Replacement)on Tuesday February 24th.   When I tell you everything was perfectly running, it was.   There were lots of patients having procedures today and thought I would  runnung a lot  longerI was in at 830 and in recovery 10:30 or 11.  Everyone on the team checked in to see how my demeanor was..  All in all if you ever need Orthopedic surgery or surgeon, HSS is top notch.",
