          "description": "Dr. Askanase is truly exceptional. You will be hard-pressed to find a rheumatologist more devoted to her patients or more passionate about advancing lupus care. She combines extraordinary medical expertise with genuine compassion, taking the time to listen, understand, and advocate for her patients. Her dedication extends far beyond the exam room, and her commitment to improving the lives of people living with lupus is evident in everything she does.",
