          "description": "HSS holds a very special place in my heart. It is a hospital that has consistently made me feel safe, cared for, and supported. The doctors and nurses are uniformly outstanding. However, I feel especially compelled to recognize my orthopedist, Dr. Mathias Bostrom, whose exceptional care and dedication truly set him apart.\nDr. Bostrom is an extraordinary physician in every sense. His clinical expertise is truly unmatched, and he combines it with genuine compassion, kindness, and patience. He always takes the time to thoroughly answer questions and thoughtfully address every concern, making his patients feel heard, respected, and cared for. Dr. Bostrom is a rare and exceptional doctor, and I cannot recommend him highly enough.",
